{"tid":1322210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 海關前關員被捕，檢獲空對空導彈","createTime":"2019-07-16T01:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T03:46:51.000Z","uid":264338,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"78adb2cbbb0f2861430666eb7b1cb619cec7ffb3","tid":1322210,"uid":264338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:17:54.000Z","msg":"意大利警方特種部隊週一（15日）在當地北部突擊搜查新納粹主義支持者的物業，起獲大批武器，當中包括一枚空對空導彈。事件中一共有三人被捕，當中包括一名曾經為極右政黨參選國會議席的海關前關員。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方調查有意大利人參與親俄武裝組織在烏克蘭東部戰事，於是派出大批警員在北部多個地方進行突擊搜查，期間在倫巴第（Lombardy）一個機場飛機庫內起獲一枚法國製空對空飛彈。警方指飛彈曾經由卡塔爾軍隊所有，經調查後證實它性能良好。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示被捕人士曾透過WhatsApp兜售飛彈。另外在調查過程中亦起獲26枝槍、20枝銃刀、306個滅聲器及瞄準器等零件，以及800多發子彈。它們主要是來自奧地利、德國和美國。除此之外，當局亦搜出一些納粹紀念品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBLw318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBLw318.jpg&h=0fe4bc86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/352342/%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%96%B0%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B-%E6%AA%A2%E7%8D%B2%E7%A9%BA%E5%B0%8D%E7%A9%BA%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F352342%2F%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25B2%25B9%25E5%258B%25A2%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25BD%2588&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=a0cad1d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/352342/%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%96%B0%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B-%E6%AA%A2%E7%8D%B2%E7%A9%BA%E5%B0%8D%E7%A9%BA%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88</a><br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp都買到飛彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><